Khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] dung[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] setInterval toen[C2:RN_AN_EN] cuc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] — lazy evaluation tai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] thau[C2:RN_OI_AU] diem[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] touch.

Vong[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] lap[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] ticks: tinh[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] so[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] ticks da[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] trau[C0:RN_OI_AU] qua va[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] apply tung[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] tick.
Day[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] la[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] cach[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] simulate continuous decay ma[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] cen[C2:RN_AN_EN] background process.
